abstract: China Life Insurance, the country’s biggest life insurer, said on Monday that it had invested $300 million in Visa‘s initial public offering in its maiden overseas investment.
lead_paragraph: China Life Insurance, the country’s biggest life insurer, said on Monday that it had invested $300 million in Visa‘s initial public offering in its maiden overseas investment.

headline.main: China Life Pours $300 Million into Visa I.P.O.
